# === Global Data Exclusions ===

# Ignore all 'data/' folders anywhere in the repo
**/data/

# === Keep metadata and documentation ===
!**/metadata/
!**/metadata/**
!**/README.txt
!**/README.md
!**/*.md
!**/*.txt

# === Ignore temporary and hidden files ===
.Rhistory
.Rproj.user/
.RData
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# === Ignore renv binary libraries (if using renv) ===
renv/library/
renv/python/

# === Ignore output and temp files ===
**/*.zip
**/*.7z
**/*.tar.gz
**/*.RData
**/*.csv
!**/metadata/*.csv  # Allow metadata CSVs

# === Logs and artifacts ===
*.log
*.aux
*.out
*.toc
